{"tid":2275244,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"侵支持者係時候起義捍衛核心價值民主同公義","createTime":"2020-11-07T04:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T07:22:23.000Z","uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"071dc746b4b5f722639af5f1af4f417d786dd5a1","tid":2275244,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"民兵起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一望無際的內華達州維京山谷，便是邦迪的牧場所在地。Photo Credit: Reuters/達志影像<br />\n為了自由，你願意走上戰場嗎？<br />\n今年4月，美國內華達州出現一起民兵起義、逼退政府的大消息。當地一名牧場主人邦迪（Cliven Bundy）因為長期在聯邦政府的土地上違法放牧，同時積欠大筆管理費，美國聯邦執法人員因而決定強制收繳邦迪的900頭牛，將牠們驅逐出聯邦土地。支持邦迪的民兵組織聞訊趕到，與警方對峙數日後，4月12日聯邦執法人員宣布撤退並釋放牛隻，待日後繼續以法院途徑解決紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/3632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F3632&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=a06b2393\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/3632</a>"},{"pid":"7a3744615338db195a8931bed57330d0a54bd49a","tid":2275244,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}